            <history-note id="DLM1008737"><amended-provision>Section 58(4)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>20 September 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM968189">section 4</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Defence Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 51).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM206418"><amended-provision>Section 58(4)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM347662">section 7(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Defence Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 49).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM1028501"><amended-provision>Section 50(4)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>20 September 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM968189">section 4</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Defence Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 51).</history-note>
