            <history-note id="DLM206419"><amended-provision>Section 58(5)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM347662">section 7(4)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Defence Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 49).</history-note>
